Ga wani gajeren jawabi a West Virginia a tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara yakin neman zabensa a birnin Willing, West Virginia, a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne jawabi na farko cikin jawabai biyar da Trump zai gabatar a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
A lokacin da ya kada kuri'ar amincewa da tsarin dakatar da takarar da ya zaba a kotun koli, Trump na neman karfafa goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe a tsakiyar shekara, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi jawabin da Trump zai yi a yammacin Virginia kuma ta yaya za mu iya kallon sa a Intane?
Za a yi jawabi a birnin Willing, a jihar West Virginia, a ƙarfe bakwai na yammacin ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon jawabin Trump a West Virginia a bidiyon da ke ƙasa.
Trump zai iya shiga cikin batun wannan makon na dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, saboda ta jefa kuri'a mai yawa game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i lokacin da Majalisar Dattawa ta amince da dakatar da gabatar da takarar har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan yakin shine  taimaka wa 'yan Republican su sami wasu ƙarfi a gaban zaɓe a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, jami'an yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump sun ce, taron na mako mai zuwa, wanda aka ruwaito daga Reuters, zai taimaka wajen karfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya, a kokarin da 'yan Republican ke yi na karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci a cikin ajanda, shugaban zai yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da dama saboda lokacin yakin neman zabe yana kan zagaye", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump da bai bayyana sunansa ba.
"Maganar da za a yi a filin wasa na West Bank da yammacin yau za ta jawo hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma daukar hankalin kafofin yada labarai na Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya samu kashi 40 cikin dari a zaben 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya yi kasa a zaben.
"Ba kyakkyawan labari ba ne ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo ya yi amfani da shi don ya hau kan mukaminsa", in ji Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
