Bayan Toyota, wasu masana'antun motoci ma sun nuna cewa ana bukatar ci gaba da amfani da tsarin samar da kayayyaki mai kyau.
Toyota ba ta iya cewa tsawon lokacin da za a dakatar da aikin ba, amma ta yi gargadin cewa a cikin dogon lokaci, ƙarin farashin zai rage gasa a masana'antar kuma a ƙarshe ya jawo farashin aiki.
