"A yayin da ake ci gaba da fafatawa kan wanda zai zama babban alkalin kotun kolin Amurka, za a iya dage wani muhimmin taro tsakanin Donald Trump da mataimakin babban lauyan kasar Rod Rosenstein na tsawon mako guda", a cewar fadar White House a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein ya jagoranci aikin mai ba da shawara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken harkar Rasha a zaben, da kuma alakar da ke tsakanin masu goyon bayan Trump da Rasha da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban gudanar da shari'a.
