Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
"Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afku a birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a", in ji jami'ai, kuma ana ganin adadin zai karu.
A sakamakon lalacewar cibiyoyin sadarwa, jami'an tsaro ba su iya samun bayanai daga yankin Donggala Regency  da ke arewacin Palau ba, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palu.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da mutanen da ke tsibirin Sulawesi.
Palu, wanda ke da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a shekara ta 2017, shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, wanda aka kafa a cikin wani ɗan gajeren gabar tekun yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haifuwarsa.
Dongala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi) a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin mulkin mallaka  a cikin ƙaramin yanki na yanki  a cikin 2017 akwai kusan mutane 299 200.
Kiwo da noma sune manyan ginshikan tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da muhimmanci a lardin, ko da yake mafi yawansa yana cikin Morovaly a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i a ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru ɗari da suka shige, tsunamis sun addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami da ya auku a Donggala ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje.
Ƙari ga haka, tsunami da ya auku a Donggala ta yamma a shekara ta 1996 ya kashe mutane tara.
A cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin Tekun Fasifik, ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a ƙasar Indonesia.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan.
A ranar 26 ga Disamba, 2004, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da ta auku a arewacin Sumatra, a lardin Aceh, a ƙasar Indonisiya, ta haddasa tsunami da ya addabi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gaɓar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
A ƙarshen watan Maris da kuma farkon watan Afrilu na shekara ta 2005, manyan girgizar ƙasa da yawa sun auku a yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Niassa da ke kusa da wurin.
A shekara ta 2006, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin tsibirin Java, babban tsibirin ƙasar Indonesia kuma ta haddasa tsunami da ya auku a gaɓar teku ta kudu kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
A shekara ta 2009, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa yankin da ke kusa da birnin Padanha, a lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
A shekara ta 2010, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai da ke kusa da Sumatra kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsayi mita 10 da ya ambaliya ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
A shekarar 2016, wata girgizar kasa mai tsanani ta lalata fadar shugaban kasar Pidija Jaya a Aceh, kuma hakan ya haifar da fargaba, saboda mutane sun tuna yadda aka lalata komai bayan mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami a shekarar 2004.
Amma, da akwai mutane fiye da 100 da suka mutu a lokacin da gine-ginen suka rushe.
A shekarar 2018, girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok da ke Indonesia, inda yawon bude ido suka fi zuwa, kuma ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a bakin tekun.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin kan zargin cin zarafin iyalansa
An kama Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, akan zargin kai hari.
Rahoton 'yan sanda na Alaska da aka fitar a ranar Asabar ya ce an kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin mata da maza da kuma hana bayar da rahoton cin zarafin mata da maza da kuma tsayayya da tsare shi.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya nuna cewa sa'ad da wata abokiyarta ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don ta gaya musu game da wasu laifuffuka, sai ya ƙwace wayar daga hannun ta.
A cewar KTUU, an mayar da Palin zuwa gidan yari na Mat-Su da ke gaban kotu don a tsare shi da takobi kuma an sake shi kan belin dalar Amurka 500.
A ranar Asabar din nan ne ya bayyana a gaban kotu inda aka nemi ya yi bayani, inda ya ce ba shi da laifi, in ji kafar yada labarai ta CNN.
An zargi Palin da laifuffuka uku na Class A, wanda ke nufin zai iya fuskantar ɗaurin shekara ɗaya da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, wanda zai iya kai shi gidan yari na kwana ɗaya da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka tuhumi Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an tuhume shi da kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa Sarah Palin ta kira 'yan sanda kuma ta ba da rahoton wani hari.
Yanzu haka, ana shari'ar ne a kotun da ke jihar Alaska.
A cikin watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da laifin kai hari a gida, hana bayar da rahoto kan aikata laifukan tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma yin amfani da makami a cikin halin rashin hankali.
Budurwarsa ta ce ya buge ta a fuska.
A shekara ta 2016, Sarah Palin ta fuskanci suka daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji bayan da ta danganta mummunan halin ɗanta da cutar damuwa da ya samu daga aikinsa a Iraki.
