Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullah Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa wani dan kasa ba tun 1953.
An yi zargin cewa a ranar 31 ga watan Oktoba, Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan hanyar yammacin Manhattan yayin da yake tafiya, yana lalata masu tafiya da masu keke.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka yi a gundumar kudu ta birnin New York, an ce masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi musu lahani.
A cewar kotu, duka laifuffukan biyu na iya jawo hukuncin kisa.
Bayan makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke hukuncin kisa a kan Saipov a kan wasu abubuwa 22, da suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai da kuma lalata dukiya (wanda ake amfani da shi a kotun tarayya a shari'ar aikata laifuka masu tsari) da kuma cin zarafi da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce an shirya harin sosai kuma an yi tunani sosai, kuma Saipov ya kira yadda ya aikata shi da kyama, zalunci da lalata.
'Ayyukan Sayfullo Habibullaevicius Saipov sun yi sanadiyar raunata, raunuka da asarar rayukan dangin wadannan mutane da kuma abokan su: Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlich, Hernano Ferruccio, Hernano Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damiano Pagnucco', in ji sanarwar.
Wadanda aka kashe biyar daga cikinsu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
An yi shari'ar kisa a Kudancin New York shekaru goma da suka shige.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan wasu masu safarar miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
An yi hukuncin kisa a shekara ta 1953 a New York a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa shekaru biyu da suka shige don ƙulla su yi leƙen asiri a ƙasar Soviet a lokacin Cold War.
An kashe Rosenberg biyu a kan 19 ga Yuni, 1953 a cikin kujera na lantarki.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, dan Uzbekistan, bai yi nadamar abin da ya yi ba nan da nan bayan harin ko watanni bayan haka.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
A cewar tuhumar, Saipov ya bayyana wa jami'an cewa bidiyon da ya kalli a wayarsa na wayar salula da ke dauke da bayanan kungiyar ISIS ne ya sa ya kai harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya kuma nemi a rataye tutar IS a dakin jinya.
Ya yi watsi da tuhumar da ake masa ta abubuwa 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin Saipov da ke da kudaden gwamnati ya ce sun yi takaicin matakin da aka dauka.
"Muna ganin yanke shawarar yanke hukuncin kisa maimakon yanke hukuncin kisa da rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai kara wa duk wanda ya shiga cikin lamarin rauni", in ji Patton.
A baya, 'yan kare Saipov sun nemi masu gabatar da kara da su guji yanke hukuncin kisa.
