Ƙungiyar 'yan wasa ta farko: Dundee Stars 5 da 3
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallo biyu a wasan da ya buga da Dundee Giants
Dundee Stars ta dawo da wasanta da Belfast Giants a gasar Premier a ranar Juma'a kuma ta lashe wasanta da Dundee da ci 5 da 3.
Giants sun tashi da wuri da ci biyu da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka ci.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita wasan kafin Dwyer ya sake jan ragamar Giants.
Francois Bouchard na Dundee ya daidaita wasan, amma daga baya Lukaku Lundwald ya ci kwallo biyu a raga.
'Yan Adam Keefe sun sha kashi na uku a gasar Premier a wannan kakar, bayan sun ci Dundee da ci 2 da 1 a Belfast a daren Juma'a.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin suka hadu a wannan kakar, kuma Giants sun lashe wasannin uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya fara bugawa a minti na hudu (3.35) bayan da Kendall McFaullow ya wuce, kuma bayan da ya ci gaba da minti hudu, Beauvillier ya ninka nasara bayan David Rutherford ya wuce.
A wasan da ya fara da wuya, Sullivan ya dawo da masu gidan wasan a wasan da ya ci gaba da cin nasara a 13:10, kuma bayan da Matt Marquardt ya ba da Cownie ya daidaita 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun shiga cikin farko da farko, kuma a ƙarshen farkon wasan ya sami nasarar cin nasara a karo na biyu na dare.
Da yake suna da ci gaba sosai, sai suka sake haɗuwa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaita wasan da 27:37.
