Labaran ambaliyar ruwa a Pineal, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida (FWC) ya ce yawan ruwan da ke tafasa a cikin ruwan teku na Tampa Bay yana raguwa.
A cewar FWC, an lura da furen da ya fi raguwa a cikin Pineellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier Counties  wannan yana nuna cewa an rage maida hankali.
Ruwan ruwan ya mamaye kusan mil 130 na bakin teku daga arewacin Paines zuwa kudancin Lee County.
Ana iya samun wuraren da ke cikin mil 10 daga bakin teku a gundumar Hillsborough, amma ba su da yawa kamar na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga ruwan sama mai ja a yankin Pasca.
